  • Classes in annexes used by annexes 
    Class and Description
    Client
    This class Client represent the subscription of a Subscriber indeed this class gather all filters for each topic that the subscriber subscribe, the ReceptionCOutBoundPort and the URI of the ReceptionCInBoundPort.
  • Classes in annexes used by components 
    Class and Description
    GestionClient
    This class GestionClient manage all subscriptions of the Broker, it's confine in this class and it use a concurrent hashmap in order to access the client information.
    TopicKeeper
    This class TopicKeeper represent the storage of all the messages of a Broker (a concurrent hashmap with topic as key and vector of message as value)
